Description: Ramping UI for 1-channel clicky-switch lights
  Ramps up and down and allows the user to stop at any level.
  Double-tap to shortcut to highest level.
  Options: Memory, stop-at-the-top, turbo timer, factory reset.
Button-Type: clicky
Memory: offtime, mem decay, configurable
MCU: attiny13
Authors: gChart, ToyKeeper
Modes: ramp, battcheck, config
Extras: LVP, ramping UI, turbo timer
License: GPLv3
